What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Laid back class, Professor has a lot of stories that are funny and cool.
A good class for thinking if you choose to take on the challenge, but otherwise very loosely structured and can get repetitious. The Monday afternoons in particular can feel very long.
I definitely recommend this class. It will cause you to step back and reflect on what is really normal or deviant.
